Idbi Bank Silapathar IFSC & Branch Info

The IFSC Code of Idbi Bank Silapathar branch is IBKL0001511. The branch is located in Dhemaji district of Assam. For address and phone numbers, scroll down.

Idbi Bank Silapathar MICR & Contact Info

Address, MICR code, branch contact number etc of IDBI Silapathar branch is given below. You may contact the branch or the Customer Care number of the bank information relating to your Idbi Bank account.

IDBI branches in Dhemaji | IDBI branches in Assam

Along with your account number, account name and account type (ie., savings or current) the following information about the branch is to be provided for fund transfer:

Bank Name : Idbi Bank

Branch Name : Silapathar

IFSC Code : IBKL0001511

Location : Silapathar, Dhemaji, Assam - View full address

To make NEFT or RTGS money transfer to Idbi Bank Silapathar branch from any other bank in India, IFSC code is necessary. For hustle free payment transfer, share the accurate IFSC, branch name and account number with the transferer.
